'''Peter Henlein''' ([[1479]]/[[1480]] - August [[1542]]) from [[Nuremberg]] is considered the inventor of the portable [[watch]]. He was also a locksmith and invented the watch's mainspring.

== Literatur ==
*J<U+00FC>rgen Abeler: ''In Sachen Peter Henlein''. Wuppertaler Uhrenmuseum, Wuppertal 1980
*Maren Winter: ''Der Stundensammler''. Wilhelm Heyne Verlag, M<U+00FC>nchen 2004 (Roman), ISBN 3-453-40146-8,

